title: Mamalicious
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Bakery, Canadian
description: Canadian diner-style restaurant. Food is vegetarian and uses faux sausage and bacon. Offers a large menu with items like BLT bagel, chilli, vegan macaroni and cheese, house-made burgers with sauces and bread. Large selection of baked goods and cakes. Open since 2011.
